codeText: @Override_	protected void validateMergedContextConfiguration(WebMergedContextConfiguration webMergedConfig) {_		if (webMergedConfig.hasClasses()) {_			String msg = String.format(_				"Test class [%s] has been configured with @ContextConfiguration's 'classes' attribute %s, "_						+ "but %s does not support annotated classes.", webMergedConfig.getTestClass().getName(),_				ObjectUtils.nullSafeToString(webMergedConfig.getClasses()), getClass().getSimpleName())__			logger.error(msg)__			throw new IllegalStateException(msg)__		}_	}
